metadata.name: RootzToken #1
metadata.description:
The RootzToken is a Soulbound NFT

      It cannot be traded or transferred... but instead
      engraves your wallet with the powers of the
      RootzTribe emblem. Providing immediate and
      long-term gains to those who commit to
      joining us on this journey.
      
      Bear or bull, the anointed members of the
      RootzTribe shall roam the realms of web3 for
      years to come... And the journey begins now.
